<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="读书人" class="zu-question-my-bio">读书人</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="222">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$nian-shi-san-96" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/nian-shi-san-96" class="zg-link" title="年十三">年十三</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-kang-de-xiao-xi-fu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-kang-de-xiao-xi-fu" class="zg-link" title="陈康的小媳妇">陈康的小媳妇</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ni-gan-qin-wo-ma" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ni-gan-qin-wo-ma" class="zg-link" title="你敢亲我吗">你敢亲我吗</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2324741" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">理性答：<br>网友写的东西，要星爷道歉，无理；<br>拉人站队用声势压人，可鄙；<br>说自己不是黑社会，又要“十天之内解释清楚否则要你好看”，荒唐。<br><br>感性答：<br>面对一场普通如我根本弄不清楚真相的口水仗，信一个名字都没听过的女人的指责，去质疑用十多年带给我欢笑的偶像，我吃饱了撑的吗？
<a href="/question/25355131/answer/30533673" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
